Initial Release.  Download the jar file and zip file. 
The zip file contains other jar dependencies:

Tidy.jar
commons-codec.jar
commons-httpclient.jar
commons-logging-api.jar
commons-logging.jar
htmlparser.jar
jargs.jar

Unzip the contents of the zipfile.  
Make sure all jar files are in the same folder, 
then run the spider by running: 

java -jar aspider-0.1a.jar

Email me if you have any problems.

Future releases will have options for downloading 
filetypes as well as mime-types.
( right now, it only matches mime types )
Also will have options for logging output options, 
right now all logging goes to stdout and stderr.

